edu.jhu.cs.oose.fall2010.invasion.iface
Interface InvasionModelListener

public interface InvasionModelListener

This interface represents a listener for an Invasion model. The model contains a collection of these listeners without specific knowledge of which implementations have been provided (allowing the model not to be dependent upon those code modules that wish to observe it). Whenever any event occurs on the model, the model will send an event object describing that event to each listener.
